Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.53,0:00:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明浪潮就已经很难对付了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然勇者之间要互相争斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.58,0:00:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为了世界我要杀掉四圣勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.96,0:00:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉四圣勇者吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.55,0:00:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.09,0:00:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.72,0:00:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.85,0:00:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们变得很粘人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.27,0:00:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.77,0:00:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,束缚风牢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.37,0:00:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔芾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.62,0:00:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.08,0:00:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.33,0:01:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对小梅尔做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.21,0:01:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔炭我要你成为人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人质怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者和我约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.56,0:03:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其他勇者友好相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小梅尔放出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.94,0:03:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不答应你就会伤害梅尔蒂是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.74,0:03:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说过了做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此菲托莉亚也要拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一定要让勇者们和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.96,0:03:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是和养育菲托莉亚的勇者定下的重要的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.55,0:03:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且为了从浪潮中拯救世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者必须互相协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.72,0:03:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.26,0:03:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你拜托几次我都不打算与他们和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.10,0:03:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为了召唤新的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚会杀掉目前的所有勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚你的话就是这个意思吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样是为了世界好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.33,0:03:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭借她的力量的确可以做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和其他勇者和解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.88,0:04:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此即使如此也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要特地抓梅尔蒂做人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.72,0:04:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想杀我就杀吧不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.89,0:04:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人-尚文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.93,0:04:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不打算毫不反抗地被你干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.57,0:04:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白盾之勇者的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.32,0:04:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.12,0:04:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就向菲牦莉亚证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.75,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只凭盾之勇者和其随从也有能够对抗浪潮的强大力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.79,0:04:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做在这里和你战斗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概知道盾之勇者有多强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和菲洛单独对战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.72,0:05:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旦菲托莉亚认同你的实力就放了梅尔炭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.65,0:05:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且会暂时放弃杀掉勇者们暂缓执行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.57,0:05:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不太懂不过只要菲洛羸了就不会杀掉主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且会放掉小梅尔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不等等菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.41,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么菲洛要打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚就用这个样子战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以菲洛也用人类的姿态战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.13,0:05:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要开始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.98,0:05:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.74,0:05:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.96,0:06:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.39,0:06:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚那家伙为什么不选拉芙塔莉雅而选了菲洛和她战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且为什么要用人形战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.02,0:06:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛不能胡乱进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多用用脑子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看准时机让衣服恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.49,0:06:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注入魔力提高一些防御力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量之源菲洛命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.75,0:06:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解读理之力用强烈的真空龙卷吹飞此人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.05,0:06:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中级咙卷风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.06,0:07:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将真空龙卷无效化反中级龙卷风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妨碍魔法小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.86,0:07:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是破绽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.79,0:07:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就没有时间恢复衣服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.71,0:07:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再下去菲洛就危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来试试能不能用盾打破围栏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文-尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然轻易把盾的防御力打破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.69,0:07:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别四处张望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.15,0:08:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们打算耍赖救梅尔炭的下场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.04,0:08:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过盾之勇者会变成这样都因为菲洛太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛是为什么战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.75,0:08:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用说嘛当然是为了主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.01,0:08:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不嬴昨天的龙也打不赢菲托莉亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.72,0:08:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能帮得了盾之勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.89,0:08:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛不会输要为了主人变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有想法是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人您没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.41,0:08:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再让主人受伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.21,0:08:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛菲洛会变得更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.84,0:08:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在从空气中聚集魔力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能做到这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.65,0:09:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.57,0:09:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来好好观察对方的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.54,0:09:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.88,0:09:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.55,0:09:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋冲击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.61,0:09:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.50,0:10:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.25,0:10:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛居然能用魔法进行那样的攻击·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.06,0:10:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人菲洛会变得更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.32,0:10:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人也好小梅尔也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅姐姐也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.57,0:10:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛会变得强大到能保护大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.54,0:10:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.21,0:11:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.01,0:11:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会放了梅尔炭你很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.23,0:11:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛赢了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯你很厉害菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮地完成了试炼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛你被试探了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.01,0:11:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错如果没能完成试炼菲洛就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者也会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.23,0:12:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.94,0:12:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是通过了菲托莉亚试炼的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低下头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.66,0:12:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛赐予你菲托莉亚的第一继承权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.71,0:12:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛会成为菲洛鸟的下任女王吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小菲洛好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.64,0:12:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是继承王位的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是呆毛嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.11,0:12:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像长了个奇怪的东西讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.86,0:12:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又长出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再怎么拔都会长出来的放弃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.37,0:12:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次成长这些毛就会变多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变成这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.42,0:13:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力增强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆毛上有增加能力的保佑功能或者什么的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的奖励对于没法提升等级的菲洛倒是不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有给盾之勇者的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有?我可不要呆毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.06,0:13:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.14,0:13:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是更好的东西我再帮你把伤治好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么将盾拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强制解放?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有很多因为等级不够而不能使用的盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.46,0:13:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但与菲洛鸟相关的盾全部开放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎只要满足条件就能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.01,0:13:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹感谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.72,0:13:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气但是我还有话要单独和盾之勇者说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.14,0:14:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我们不止是为了试探小菲洛而被利用的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.69,0:14:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯对不起梅尔炭你有什么想要的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.41,0:14:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦那那就那个那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.09,0:14:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像做梦一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙就要这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛也想快点长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.98,0:14:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道到时候呆毛会变成多少根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.83,0:15:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天才刚开始你们好好休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.91,0:15:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.88,0:15:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然菲托莉亚都那么说了那就照办吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开庆祝会并且再次欢迎大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.81,0:15:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庆祝新女王的诞生?是指菲洛吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.10,0:15:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别擅自决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你小菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要一起吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续白天的话题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.04,0:16:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的曾经打算和他们友好相处?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.63,0:16:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是这事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经打算洗清自己的嫌疑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.98,0:17:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或许是放弃了觉得他们不可能相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.99,0:17:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不确切否定的话就相当于承认了罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的也有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚将你们带出这里时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.58,0:17:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算把你们放在离其他四圣勇者比较近的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要跟着我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚不会继续插手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能拿出让我最后插手的价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.64,0:17:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了你要我把话都说清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.27,0:17:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽可能妥善处理说完了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.94,0:17:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.40,0:17:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在四圣勇者哪怕缺少一人的情况下迎来浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,届时防御浪潮就会变得相对困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此杀掉所有四圣勇者重新召唤才是为了这个世界好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.37,0:17:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不四个人好好交流互相和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们左右都会被你杀掉是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是在第几次浪潮之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.26,0:18:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但世界强迫所有生命牺牲的那一刻会降临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界强迫所有生命牺牲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.02,0:18:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者会被迫选择是否要参加这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚在等待那个时刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.52,0:18:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了众人而战还是为了世界而战二选
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.65,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果选为了世界而战那么将牺牲许多生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.87,0:18:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此仍然可以完成使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.91,0:18:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果选择为了众人会怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.75,0:18:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充满荆棘的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底知道多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.13,0:18:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚也忘记了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.97,0:18:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救世界和拯救众人是不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.73,0:18:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的勇者曾经希望后世的勇者选择拯救众人的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.65,0:19:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听不太懂不过身为勇者就应该选这条路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这样不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有盾之勇者一个人难以战胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说为什么要找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.87,0:19:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去说服其他勇者或许更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.17,0:19:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起其他勇者菲托莉亚更看好盾之勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.93,0:19:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,养育了新女王菲洛的盾之勇者不可能是坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就当你是坏人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.69,0:19:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚觉得盾之勇者有和其他勇者好好交流的气量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且四圣勇者太过弱小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.32,0:19:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去哪怕不用菲托莉亚出手你们不久就会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.33,0:19:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后的战斗那么艰难吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.04,0:20:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就更加需要愤怒之盾的力量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.50,0:20:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你必须要使用那面盾的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.80,0:20:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以抑制诅咒之盾的侵蚀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.10,0:20:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不能完全抑制还是尽量不要用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.77,0:20:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口口声声说要杀了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果菲托莉亚你还挺温柔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.57,0:20:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚真温柔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.08,0:20:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你帮了那么多忙我就尽可能试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过别太期待了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.47,0:20:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了盾之勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.39,0:21:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说养育你的难道是盾之勇者?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.10,0:21:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记了菲洛鸟很健忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.99,0:21:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还记得这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.51,0:23:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.77,0:23:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是四圣武器的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.11,0:23:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯不会错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.04,0:23:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.00,0:23:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面是空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.63,0:23:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位快逃
